{
  "stem": "18932.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because every time that the people came, that we heard that the Germans are coming to look for people, we used to hide in that little-- there was a little tiny-- it was like a little house but with one room, more like a storage room.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then me and my mom used to hide when we heard that the Germans were coming.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we were laying underneath a headboard under the window.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So when the Germans would look in, they wouldn't see us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that's how we were hiding, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember that, because we left before that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as I told you, I was-- I was working in the carpet factory.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then after a short while, they disbanded it and sent all the young children to a other factory, in a factory that were makings, I think, believe, was uniforms for the Germans, and we worked there.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And from there, there was-- the German ask the director of this factory occasionally to give him names, people they should evacuate.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one day, there was a list, and my name was on this list.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I knew that I have to hide unless they come and-- and look for me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had an uncle which was a policeman in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when I saw the name, I went to him and I asked him, please, could you do something?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, the director of the place, they should take off my name from the list.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he did, and he managed to take off my name.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But unfortunately for me, my name was typed twice, and my-- the other name was still on this list.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one day they came to look for me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was on-- we were in this little place that we were.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
